    "These ML-driven insights can be used for downstream tasks such as forecasting, prediction, and control.",
    "In this work, we explore the growing application of ML in smart building systems, and examine how ML-based solutions often match or outperform more traditional methods.",
    "Prior studies related to this paper (Rupp et al., 2015; Wang and Hong, 2020; Zhang et al., 2021; Zhao et al., 2021) mainly focus on review studies in a subdomain.",
